uk.co.optimisticpanda.gtest.dto.defaultfill
Class ValueGeneratorCache

java.lang.Object
  uk.co.optimisticpanda.gtest.dto.defaultfill.ValueGeneratorCache

public class ValueGeneratorCache
extends java.lang.Object

This is used to store IEdits used for filling newly created dtos with default data

IEdits can be registered at different levels as they are looked up in the following order:

  1. property path (ognl/el style notation)
  2. The class, the name and the property type
  3. The property name and the property type.
  4. The property type
  5. return a NullEdit

Author:
Andy Lee
